ZH: 我需要向老板汇报这个项目的进展情况。
EN: I need to report the progress of this project to my boss.

ZH: 她每天都会向上级汇报工作情况。
EN: She reports her work situation to her superiors every day.

ZH: 他们被要求每周一次向团队汇报工作内容。
EN: They are required to report their work to the team once a week.

ZH: 请你写一份周报汇报你的工作。
EN: Please write a weekly report to update your work.

ZH: 经理总是准时汇报每个月的销售数据。
EN: The manager always reports the monthly sales figures on time.

ZH: 我们需要向总经理汇报我们的客户满意度。
EN: We need to report our customer satisfaction to the CEO.

ZH: 警方定期向市长汇报治安问题。
EN: The police regularly report the public security issues to the mayor.

ZH: 请你向全体员工汇报关于公司改革的计划。
EN: Please report the company's reform plan to all employees.

ZH: 每隔一段时间，我们会向投资人汇报公司的财务状况。
EN: From time to time, we report the company's financial status to our investors.

ZH: 我们的团队汇报了最新的市场调查结果。
EN: Our team reported the latest market research findings.

ZH: 他们需汇报关于产品开发的进度。
EN: They need to report the progress of product development.

ZH: 下周会议上，请你汇报销售数据。
EN: Please report the sales data at the meeting next week.

ZH: 他每月都要汇报他的工作给上级。
EN: He reports his work to his superiors every month.

ZH: 我需要你以电子邮件的形式向我汇报每天的工作进展。
EN: I need you to report your daily work progress to me via email.

ZH: 请大家花一点时间准备好汇报材料。
EN: Please take some time to prepare the materials for the presentation.

ZH: 我们汇报了新产品的市场反馈情况。
EN: We reported the market feedback of the new product.

ZH: 他被要求在会议上汇报他的研究成果。
EN: He is required to report his research findings at the meeting.

ZH: 我们将在下个月的会议上向大家汇报项目的进展。
EN: We will report the progress of the project to everyone at the meeting next month.

ZH: 请你在每个季度的结束时向总裁汇报部门的表现。
EN: Please report the performance of your department to the CEO at the end of each quarter.

ZH: 我们会在明天的会议上向大家汇报最新的市场竞争情况。
EN: We will report the latest market competition situation to everyone at tomorrow's meeting.
